The '''first Church of the Dark Side''' was the first ever church constructed by the [[Church of the Dark Side]] dedicated to their false religion. It was opened on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] following the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]] by the false [[Prophets of the Dark Side]], as a way to control the masses.

